  <num>38-901</num>
  <heading>Whole school-day sessions.</heading>
  <text>All children of school age being instructed in the schools of the District beyond the 2nd grade shall be given a whole school-day session.</text>
  <annotations>
    <annotation type="History" doc="Stat. 59-1-ch3446" path="§1">June 20, 1906, 34 Stat. 316, ch. 3446, § 1</annotation>
